[0.129.0]
* Initial public packaging for Cloudron: unified SigNoz v0.129.0 stack (ZooKeeper, ClickHouse, SigNoz, OTel collector v0.144.5).
* Addons: localstorage, postgresql (metadata), sendmail (alert SMTP).
* OTLP TCP ports 4317/4318; health check `GET /api/v1/health`.
* Automated upstream watch and catalog publishing via GitHub Actions.
